            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿مُخْلِصًا لَهُ الدِّينَ﴾ مُوَحِّدًا لَهُ العِبَادَةَ وَالطَّاعَةَ.</p>"
        },
        "3": {
            "verses": {
                "39:3": {
                    "id": 3
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿الدِّينُ الْخَالِصُ﴾ الطَّاعَةُ التَّامَّةُ السَّالِمَةُ مِنَ الشِّرْكِ.</p>\n<h2>﴿زُلْفَى﴾ تَقَرُّبًا.</h2>"
        },
        "4": {
            "verses": {
                "39:4": {
                    "id": 4
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿لاَصْطَفَى﴾ لاَخْتَارَ.</h2>"
        },
        "5": {
            "verses": {
                "39:5": {
                    "id": 5
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿يُكَوِّرُ﴾ يُدْخِلُ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿وَسَخَّرَ﴾ ذَلَّلَ.</h2>\n<p>﴿الْعَزِيزُ﴾ الغَالِبُ عَلَى أَمْرِهِ، المُنْتَقِمُ مِنْ أَعْدَائِهِ.</p>"
        },
        "6": {
            "verses": {
                "39:6": {
                    "id": 6
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿ثَمَانِيَةَ أَزْوَاجٍ﴾ ثَمَانِيَةَ أَنْوَاعٍ ذُكُورًا وإِنَاثًا؛ مِنَ الإِبِلِ وَالبَقَرِ وَالضَّأْنِ وَالمَعْزِ.</p>\n<h2>﴿خَلْقًا مِنْ بَعْدِ خَلْقٍ﴾ طَوْرًا مِنْ بَعْدِ طَوْرٍ.</h2>\n<p>﴿فِي ظُلُمَاتٍ ثَلاَثٍ﴾ ظُلْمَةِ البَطْنِ، وَالرَّحِمِ، وَالمَشِيمَةِ.</p>\n<p>﴿فَأَنَّى تُصْرَفُونَ﴾ كَيْفَ تَعْدِلُونَ عَنْ عِبَادَتِهِ؟!</p>"
        },
        "7": {
            "verses": {
                "39:7": {
                    "id": 7
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿وَلاَ تَزِرُ وَازِرَةٌ﴾ لاَ تَحْمِلُ نَفْسٌ آثِمَةٌ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿وِزْرَ أُخْرَى﴾ إِثْمَ نَفْسٍ أُخْرَى.</h2>"
        },
        "8": {
            "verses": {
                "39:8": {
                    "id": 8
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿مُنِيبًا إِلَيْهِ﴾ رَاجِعًا إِلَيْهِ، مُسْتَغِيثًا بِهِ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿خَوَّلَهُ﴾ أَعْطَاهُ وَمَنَحَهُ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿أَنْدَادًا﴾ شُرَكَاءَ، وَأَمْثَالاً.</h2>"
        },
        "9": {
            "verses": {
                "39:9": {
                    "id": 9
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿قَانِتٌ﴾ مُطِيعٌ خَاضِعٌ لِلَّهِ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿آنَاءَ اللَّيْلِ﴾ سَاعَاتِ اللَّيْلِ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿أُولُو الأَلْبَابِ﴾ أَصْحَابُ العُقُولِ السَّدِيدَةِ.</h2>"
        },
        "10": {
            "verses": {
                "39:10": {
                    "id": 10
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿يُوَفَّى﴾ يُعْطَى وَافِيًا.</h2>\n<p>﴿بِغَيْرِ حِسَابٍ﴾ لاَ يُحَاسَبُونَ، أَوْ لاَ نِهَايَةَ لِمَا يُعْطَوْنَ.</p>"
        },
