            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿وَأَنِيبُوا﴾ ارْجِعُوا إِلَى اللهِ بِالتَّوْبَةِ، وَالطَّاعَةِ.</p>\n<h2>﴿وَأَسْلِمُوا﴾ اخْضَعُوا، وَانْقَادُوا.</h2>"
        },
        "55": {
